<section class="nouns-view">
  <div class="nouns-card">
    <header class="nouns-header">
      <span class="nouns-chip">⌐◨-◨ Nouns Amigos</span>
      <h1>Residencia sonora con Kbalah Radio</h1>
      <p>
        Sesiones, archivos y colaboraciones construidas junto a la comunidad Nouns. Escucha el stream dedicado y descubre los episodios especiales.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="nouns-audio">
      <audio src="https://stream.p-node.org/contretemps.mp3" controls preload="none"></audio>
      <p class="nouns-help">Si deja de sonar, recarga la página o abre el player en una nueva pestaña.</p>
      <a class="nouns-link" href="https://radio.noisk8.xyz/episodios" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
        Ver episodios
        <span class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-long" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .nouns-view {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 12rem);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .nouns-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2.4rem;
    border: 1.5px solid rgb(var(--color-border-ink));
    background: rgb(var(--color-bg-card));
    box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 rgba(var(--shadow-soft) / 0.16);
    padding: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    max-width: 42rem;
  }

  .nouns-header {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .nouns-chip {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0.55rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1.5px solid rgb(var(--color-border-ink));
    background: rgb(var(--color-primary-yellow));
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgb(var(--color-text-heading));
    box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 rgba(var(--shadow-soft) / 0.16);
  }

  .nouns-header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgb(var(--color-text-heading));
  }

  .nouns-header p {
    color: rgb(var(--color-text-muted));
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .nouns-audio {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.2rem;
  }

  .nouns-audio audio {
    width: 100%;
    border: 1.5px solid rgb(var(--color-border-ink));
    background: rgb(var(--color-bg-elevated));
    padding: 0.6rem;
  }

  .nouns-help {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgb(var(--color-text-muted));
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .nouns-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    width: fit-content;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.3rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1.5px solid rgb(var(--color-border-ink));
    background: rgb(var(--color-bg-card));
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgb(var(--color-text-heading));
    box-shadow: 5px 5px 0 rgba(var(--shadow-soft) / 0.12);
  }
</style>
